```{r echo=F, include=F, message=F, warning=F}
library(tidyverse)
files <- list.files() %>% grep("html", ., value = T) %>% grep("index.html", ., value = T, invert = T)

```


# Reports

```{r, results='asis', echo = F}

for(x in files){
cat(paste0("- [", str_remove_all(x, ".html"), "](",x,")\n"))
}

```
